These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, hot-chocolate, water
There 4 different types of food: orange, eggplant, tomato, lime
The people have 4 different hobbies: taxid-games, reading, writing, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, writer, coach, dancer
4 different pets are kept: cat, turtle, rabbit, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, skiing, ice-hockey
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, taxi, skateboard, van
 1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating lime##1
 3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who's sport is golf##1
 5. the engineer is on the right of the coach##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 7. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
11. the person driving the van is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person eating lime##2
13. the person driving the van is the person who's hobby is taxid-games##1
14. the person drinking water is the owner of the rabbit##1
15. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
17. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | water   | lemonade            | cola | hot-chocolate        |
| Food        | eggplant       | tomato         | lime     | orange       |
| Hobby       | reading     | taxid-games        | rock-climbing     | writing |
| Job         | writer     | dancer | coach    | engineer   |
| Pet         | rabbit    | snake         | cat        | turtle         |
| Sport       | ice-hockey    | cycling       | skiing    | golf     |
| Transport   | skateboard | van     | taxi         | roller         |

