 2. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is soccer and the owner of the rat##2
 3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the italian##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is the person eating mango##1
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person eating mango##1
 8. the journalist is the person eating nectarine##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the chinese and the person who's sport is cricket##2
10. the designer is on the left of the coach##1
11. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
12. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
13. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
14. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
15. the pakistani is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
16. the person watching epic movies is the italian##1
