The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, spy, scientific, martial-arts
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, chinchilla, fish, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, baseball, cricket, tennis
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking fanta is the designer##1
 3. the person eating peas is the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
 6. the accountant is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
10. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
12. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is tennis##1
13. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the owner of the fish##1
15. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
16. the person watching martial-arts movies is the mechanic##1
17. the person watching spy movies is the designer##1
18. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person eating peas##1

